  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个时序图，展示runWhileNotFindAStopPoint这个核心流程的执行机制。关键点是它分为同步执行阶段和异步提交阶段，中间用UnitOfWork来累积状态变更。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "runWhileNotFindAStopPoint",
        "UnitOfWork",
        "estado",
        "tarefas",
        "eventos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以Core是主执行器，UoW在内存中暂存所有变更。那提交的时候是谁来负责持久化？是Core直接调数据库，还是通过Repository？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "UnitOfWork",
        "Repository",
        "MongoDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "通过Repository。Core只负责执行业务逻辑和创建UoW，真正的commit交给ProcessExecutionRepository，它再和MongoDB交互。这样分层比较清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "ProcessExecutionRepository",
        "commit",
        "MongoDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，我梳理一下参与者：kikwi-core（标注runWhileNotFindAStopPoint）、UnitOfWork（注明em memória）、ProcessExecutionRepository、MongoDB，还有一个EventPublisher也是内存中的对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "UnitOfWork",
        "ProcessExecutionRepository",
        "MongoDB",
        "EventPublisher"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，EventPublisher也是em memória。注意流程分两段：第一段Core自己执行同步任务，同时往UoW里accumula各种变更；第二段才是commit和发布事件。两段之间要加个note标注\"Fim do bloco síncrono\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "UnitOfWork",
        "acumula",
        "estado",
        "tarefas",
        "eventos",
        "Fim do bloco síncrono"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我先画前半段：Core-Core的自调用表示\"Executa tarefas síncronas\"，然后Core创建UoW，接着是acumula变更。这样对吗？",
