    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正。现在画后半段：Core调用Repository的commit，Repository开启MongoDB事务，事务里分三步：atualiza ProcessInstance、cria/apaga ExecutableTasks、insere criticalEvents到event_outbox。最后返回commit成功。",
      "elements_involved": [
