    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "改好了。最后是事件发布部分：Core调用Publisher的publishEvents，传入的是unitOfWork.lightweightEvents()，然后Publisher立即返回。这里用异步箭头表示fire-and-forget？",
      "elements_involved": [
